<h2 class="bold font-l">I've Got a Cold in My Nose</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Betty Boop describes shenanigans that resulted from having a cold. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SickEpisode" class='trope-example-link'>Sick Episode</a></p>
